__Slice__.slice_name: aqm-1: Total AQM sensors in vadodara

__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT 
id, __time,
AVG(airTemperature) as airTemperature,
AVG(ambientNoise) as ambientNoise,
AVG(co) as co,
AVG(co2) as co2,
AVG(illuminance) as illuminance,
AVG(no2) as no2,
AVG(o3) as o3,
AVG(pm10) as pm10,
AVG(pm2p5) as pm2p5,
AVG(relativeHumidity) as relativeHumidity,
AVG(uv) as uv
FROM 
"vadodara-aqm"
GROUP BY __time, id
